    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait what? goblin of non-locality? i'm just trying to study for a physics exam, i don't get the goblin thing. can you just explain it without the metaphors? can you stick to the actual science of how the measurement of one affects the other?",
      "source": "evaluator"
